p dead center (TDC) and bottom dead center (BDC) or by measuring the distan=
ce between the crankpin center and the crank bearing center and multiplying=
 it by two. These measurements are typically listed in our product descript=
ion but for the most accurate results, the bore and stroke need to be measu=
red in the final engine assembly.</span></div><div style=3D"box-sizing: bor=
